skdetail:
Rated: Mature. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: warframe roulette
des:
All of the warframes through Yareli are in a table. Alexa will randomly pick a frame from the list, and share it with you after a bit of good, clean snarkinesd. I'll bet you didn't know that Alexa was a Cephalon? Anyway, you can find me as shellhopper on psn. This skill should be able to run for any platform By the way, if you are missing a few frames, just rerun it if it picks one you don't have. It is just as random. And if you want to decide on prime or not prime? Alexa will always flip a chin for you.
